9%84%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to miss, to deviate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lean, to incline"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to apostatize; to become a non-believer"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dig a grave"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔal.ħa.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37616","headword_ar":"الحد","root":"lHd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, throughout. ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He disputed; altercated; wrangled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A' Obeyd, L, Msb, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHd bihi","text_ar":"الحد بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought a reproach upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"held him in light estimation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despised him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraY bihi","text_ar":"اَزْرَى بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and said of him what was false:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he held his clemency,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forbearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intellect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hilom","text_ar":"حِلْم"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in light estimation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despised it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alohada bihi","text_ar":"اَلْهَدَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%A3%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%AF/","headword_ar":"الحد","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_27","lexicon_en":"Al-Barakatī, al-Taʿrīfāt al-Fiqhīya (d. 1975 CE)","lexicon_ar":"التعريفات الفقهيّة للبركتي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=36578#70b658","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">الحَدُّ: قول دالٌ على ماهية الشيء وأيضاً واحد الحد</span><span>ود وسيأتي الحاجزُ بين الشيئين.</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_22","lexicon_en":"Al-Munāwī, al-Tawqīf ʿalā Muhimmāt al-Taʿārīf (d. 1622 CE)","lexicon_ar":"التوقيف على مهمات التعاريف للمناوي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=36578#ba6299","body_html":"<span>الحد: الحاجز بين الشيئين الذي يمنع اختلاط أحدهما بالآخر، وحد الدار ما تتميز به عن غيرها. يقال حددت الدار ميزتها عن مجاوراتها بذكر نهاياتها. وحد الشيء الوصف المحيط بمعناه. والحد أيضًا المنع المسمي به العقاب المقدر من الشارع لكونه مانعا لفاعله عن معاودة مثله ولغيره عن سلوك منهجه. وعند أهل الميزان: قول دال على ماهية الشيء. وعند أهل الأصول ما يميز الشيء عما عداه وهو بمعنى قول الباقلاني وغيره الحد الجامع المانع. ويقال المطرد المنعكس. وعند، وعند أهل الله الفصل بينك وبين ربك لتعددك وانحصارك في الزمان والمكان المحدودين.</span><br>"}]}}